{"tid":2021440,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[OMG] 中美角力加劇,OMA只賣出6成","createTime":"2020-05-17T17:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T03:30:20.000Z","uid":73269,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"75456a335d2aaa0b73fc51abec786cd0304a1785","tid":2021440,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:30:00.000Z","msg":"中美角力近日明顯加劇中, 示威6-7月又再度活躍, 疫情又分分鐘隨住各地解封 / 冬天再臨而再度失控, 如果黎緊經濟仲無乜改善, 加上新盤突然大量增加, 樓市下行風險將會大幅提言, 相信發展商又要暗中出高回佣呢招去貨, 即係大把平野執..... <br />\n<br />\nOMA首輪沽60%<br />\n上午9時，登記時間所見，有逾百名準買家陸續到場，場內出現人龍，人潮接近1小時才散去，令抽籤時間順延約半小時。市場消息指，項目最終獲逾160枱客到場，藝人側田亦有到場陪同朋友揀樓。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190701/20717302\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190701%2F20717302&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=d5da0b46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190701%2F20717302&h=71addc1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190701/20717302</a>"},{"pid":"38eda6c00fb723d315e2e9ddc6ae73a19bd7bc11","tid":2021440,"uid":136797,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:32:59.000Z","msg":"正常人都買WETLAND <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cfac2ce6d4ea7694e7fdc9d475c0fea9084d751","tid":2021440,"uid":73269,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:34:20.000Z","msg":"Grand Marini 近年銷情最差<br />\ni只售出34%<br />\n市場消息指，Grand Marini首日售出133伙，Marini則單日售出46伙，分別佔推售量73%及34%；Grand Marini首日售134伙，屬一手新例推出後，日出康城區內首日銷情最差新盤，過往的區內新盤大部份即日沽清，未來該區尚有數個新盤準備推出，購買力或逐漸飽和。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20190911/X6QPKTU6B67HX4MQBCKR62NOCM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20190911%2FX6QPKTU6B67HX4MQBCKR62NOCM%2F&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=feeb86f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20190911%2FX6QPKTU6B67HX4MQBCKR62NOCM%2F&h=d7121a72\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20190911/X6QPKTU6B67HX4MQBCKR62NOCM/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/c7GYdyDlwvAH61b_wn3rYJrES3o=/802x599/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/CLIWIWN3YAQIIADCQI6RNTSH6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fc7GYdyDlwvAH61b_wn3rYJrES3o%3D%2F802x599%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FCLIWIWN3YAQIIADCQI6RNTSH6U.jpg&h=be47c9e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨日售樓處同場加映「求婚環節」，有人買樓後即場求婚，令女方感動流淚，圍觀人士更拍手祝賀。"},{"pid":"5003d88a1000d6d25d05f0f29ad572514f4fa7f8","tid":2021440,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:40:26.000Z","msg":"施永青 : 估全年樓價跌1成 , 但真係跌唔落, 預期年中前<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">追回今年全部跌幅</span></span>"},{"pid":"834a5833c04e82eab5cb1dd19b8a65bf97c3db91","tid":2021440,"uid":217838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:49:49.000Z","msg":"則田係咪轉左行做AA？成日係樓盤出現"},{"pid":"fef0bf1ea8f4be50698485aaae7e33299791e415","tid":2021440,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"834a5833c04e82eab5cb1dd19b8a65bf97c3db91","tid":2021440,"uid":217838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:49:49.000Z","msg":"則田係咪轉左行做AA？成日係樓盤出現"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:51:39.000Z","msg":"陪同朋友"},{"pid":"1a5aba36711b6dd8edb229a7e1f142998e82c94f","tid":2021440,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fef0bf1ea8f4be50698485aaae7e33299791e415","tid":2021440,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"834a5833c04e82eab5cb1dd19b8a65bf97c3db91","tid":2021440,"uid":217838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:49:49.000Z","msg":"則田係咪轉左行做AA？成日係樓盤出現"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:51:39.000Z","msg":"陪同朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:59:24.000Z","msg":"佢好似成日有買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b5c375cb213c61b821016e7c65d835fb0825af","tid":2021440,"uid":73269,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T18:06:37.000Z","msg":"中美角力加劇<br />\n[創新低] 大埔嘉熙月租8900元 再創白石角新低<br />\n大埔白石角有3個全新盤相繼在半年內入伙，涉及3400伙，租盤競爭甚劇烈，剛收樓的嘉熙開放式單位愈租愈平，由3月下旬首次跌穿1萬關口，至今再跌穿9000元關口。市場消息透露，嘉煕6座低層H室，實用面積248平方呎，開放式間隔，業主原本叫價1.1萬元放盤，由於租盤競爭大最終減價19%，以8900元租出，屬白石角區租盤首次跌穿9000元水平，與大埔嵐山開放式單位租金相若。業主於2018年以515萬元購入，租金回報僅2.1厘。<br />\n資料顯示，嘉熙自3月開始收樓以來，市場已錄得約70宗租務成交，當中有約15個開放式單位月租跌穿1萬元水平。開放單位月租介乎8900至1.1萬之間。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">租租win!</span></span>"},{"pid":"5f7ec9ee28c17d4a74d6510e55a3ad3f5a65d029","tid":2021440,"uid":76745,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T18:08:52.000Z","msg":"唱啖唔係咁唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd70157400e5332491de350c31bbe97bf6f5dad","tid":2021440,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f7ec9ee28c17d4a74d6510e55a3ad3f5a65d029","tid":2021440,"uid":76745,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T18:08:52.000Z","msg":"唱啖唔係咁唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T18:09:57.000Z","msg":"教我"},{"pid":"44420f3f24da90006da1486a00b576bbda75fde9","tid":2021440,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4cfac2ce6d4ea7694e7fdc9d475c0fea9084d751","tid":2021440,"uid":73269,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T17:34:20.000Z","msg":"Grand Marini 近年銷情最差<br />\ni只售出34%<br />\n市場消息指，Grand Marini首日售出133伙，Marini則單日售出46伙，分別佔推售量73%及34%；Grand Marini首日售134伙，屬一手新例推出後，日出康城區內首日銷情最差新盤，過往的區內新盤大部份即日沽清，未來該區尚有數個新盤準備推出，購買力或逐漸飽和。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20190911/X6QPKTU6B67HX4MQBCKR62NOCM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20190911%2FX6QPKTU6B67HX4MQBCKR62NOCM%2F&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=feeb86f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20190911%2FX6QPKTU6B67HX4MQBCKR62NOCM%2F&h=d7121a72\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20190911/X6QPKTU6B67HX4MQBCKR62NOCM/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/c7GYdyDlwvAH61b_wn3rYJrES3o=/802x599/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/CLIWIWN3YAQIIADCQI6RNTSH6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fc7GYdyDlwvAH61b_wn3rYJrES3o%3D%2F802x599%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FCLIWIWN3YAQIIADCQI6RNTSH6U.jpg&h=be47c9e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨日售樓處同場加映「求婚環節」，有人買樓後即場求婚，令女方感動流淚，圍觀人士更拍手祝賀。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T22:26:40.000Z","msg":"側田有無旁邊唱歌贈慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f36680c941f57ed8e71611b796ea63fbed42de9","tid":2021440,"uid":35950,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T22:42:10.000Z","msg":"永泰地產鍾志霖表示，OMA by the Sea今日公開發售，市場反應理想， 截至今晚9時已揀選約200伙，佔首輪推售268伙的逾七成。連同OMA by the Sea，本周末一手市場錄得逾320宗成交，較上周170宗急增近九成，屬逾4個月最旺。"},{"pid":"1f1072c4ae84fa3afe180253c193e801c3e0c4fc","tid":2021440,"uid":144843,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T00:46:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfd864523b6b0e63667af78ad90763913c1adbc0","tid":2021440,"uid":116659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T00:53:48.000Z","msg":"old news<br />\n新聞係19年